;　GET_GIFTDATA(GIFT_ID, "場所")    The location that the gift was bought at.
;　GET_GIFTDATA(GIFT_ID, "形容詞")  The associated adjectives (see 贈り物_形容詞.erb)
;　GET_GIFTDATA(GIFT_ID, "本体")    The price of the gift (see 贈り物_本体.erb)
